he was nowhere near your car."],[4750,4863,"No way she could of done that."],[4863,5034,"Uh, did I ask you?"],[5092,5180,"Who do you think you are"],[5180,5276,"lecturing me?"],[5288,5488,"Do you even know who I am?"],[5622,5764,"Regardless Ma'am, you just can't-"],[6010,6139,"I asked you a question."],[6272,6423,"I guess you didn't know the answer."],[6452,6731,"We're at the Stone Mansion, right?"],[6744,6894,"Do you know who your boss is?"],[7002,7123,"Yes, Mr. Stone."],[7140,7240,"And guess who I am?"],[7332,7565,"I am his fucking fiancée."],[7607,7807,"So that means I can have you fired."],[7849,7899,"Just"],[7920,7995,"like"],[8016,8087,"that."]],"18":[[112,183,"What?"],[225,279,"Ma'am-"],[279,333,"Ah!"],[1017,1142,"What the hell are you looking at?"],[1159,1217,"Go away!"],[1343,1384,"You."],[1430,1622,"Do you know how much my car costs?"],[1739,2039,"Hundreds of thousands of dollars."],[2060,2231,"So how do you propose"],[2231,2364,"to pay me back, huh?"],[2460,2556,"I, I don't know."],[2556,2686,"We don't have any money."],[2702,2831,"Is that so?"],[2982,3311,"Well, I guess we could call it even,"],[3349,3591,"if you let me scratch your face."],[3603,3712,"How would you like your looks"],[3712,3799,"to be ruined, huh?"],[4241,4291,"No."],[4375,4458,"Let go!"],[4517,4583,"Let go of me! - No."],[4583,4675,"You filthy cripple!"],[4675,4750,"Ugh."],[5075,5130,"No!"],[5376,5476,"I'm sorry, Mommy,"],[5476,5622,"I need to lie a little bit"],[5622,5722,"to protect you."],[5755,5960,"I, I'll pay you back,"],[6010,6168,"but you can't hit Mommy."],[6239,6460,"I thought you didn't have any money."],[6502,6690,"I don't, but,"],[6777,7065,"I know someone who does."],[7136,7390,"If you let us go, I'll ask him."],[7444,7486,"Oh."],[7545,7620,"Who's this,"],[7653,7874,"mysterious, nice, rich,"],[7874,8041,"person who's gonna pay me, huh?"],[8279,8404,"The man you just fought with,"],[8429,8575,"that's Raphael Stone."],[8637,8792,"He owns everything around here."],[8883,9013,