arlotte."],[5522,5676,"I heard she's such a sweetheart."],[5676,5868,"If it weren't for that brat,"],[5889,6039,"I'd be the life of the party."],[6051,6164,"But they hate us now."],[6222,6327,"Oh, I don't know what's gotten"],[6327,6498,"into Raphael,"],[6523,6756,"waiting on a cripple hand and foot."],[6756,6873,"It's absurd."],[6956,7052,"Good thing"],[7052,7248,"that won't happen for much longer."],[7248,7323,"Hmm."],[7361,7595,"Do you have what I asked you to bring?"],[7724,7828,"Of course."]],"53":[[41,296,"Do you have what I asked you to bring?"],[408,513,"Of course."],[546,638,"I've been"],[646,863,"at this game longer than you."],[880,1046,"All we need to do is feed"],[1046,1238,"those people one little lie,"],[1238,1434,"and then they will renounce"],[1434,1693,"those loyalties like that."],[1960,2127,"Once I put you in my drink,"],[2127,2277,"I'll blame it on Charlotte."],[2314,2523,"Then no one will be on her side anymore."],[5626,5739,"Ahhh!"],[5772,5860,"What is that?"],[5876,6035,"Is that a cockroach?"]],"54":[[37,208,"Oh, is that a cockroach?"],[208,296,"Oh my gosh,"],[296,392,"gross!"],[392,633,"I'm so sorry, Ms. Lawrence."],[646,796,"I don't know how it got in here."],[804,946,"Our kitchens are pristine."],[946,1084,"I don't know where that bug came from."],[1084,1288,"I know the Stones hate me,"],[1288,1484,"but I didn't expect"],[1484,1714,"even the servants to humiliate me."],[1714,1926,"On Charlotte's birthday, no less."],[1926,2031,"It's disgusting!"],[2031,2223,"The Stones are always targeting you,"],[2223,2385,"over and over again!"],[2385,2544,"Regina messed up once, but"],[2544,2686,"this is taking it a little overboard."],[2686,2857,"I mean, yeah, she's still an heiress."],[2857,3023,"She deserves some basic respect."],[3023,3103,"No, Miss,"],[3103,3278,"we would have never done that to you."],[3278,3365,"Someone must have"],[3365,3461,"put it in your drink."],[3482,3741,"Who could be so low,"],[3741,3899,"and disgusting"],[3903,4045,"as to put a cockroach"],[4045,4129,"in my drink?"],[4329,4587,"Except maybe someone"],[4587,4746,"who spent their life"],[4746,4950,"rooting through dumpsters!"],[4971,5038,"I,"],[5092,5184,"I didn't do it."],[5184,5334,"I'm scared of bugs."],[5392,5559,"We'll see about that."]],"55":[[775,880,"Ah, oh!"],[892,1021,"There are more on her."],[1113,1159,"How awful!"],[1159,1355,"What a disgusting prank!"],[1355,1534,"I mean, she's just a kid, but still."],[1543,1659,"My kids would never."],[1722,1860,"I guess old habits die hard."],[1918,2002,"You can't expect a child"],[2002,2177,"who grew up in the streets to change."],[2177,2273,"No, I didn't."],[2273,2389,"I promise!"],[2427,2560,"You think it's fun?"],[2619,2848,"Putting bugs in people's drinks?"],[2915,3044,"And you think because you're"],[3044,3249,"Raphael's little princess,"],[3249,3407,"you can get away with it?"],[3449,3607,"Well, what if..."],[3670,3916,"I do the same thing"],[3937,4020,"to you?"]],"56":[[16,145,"No, please!"],[145,312,"Don't come any closer!"],[312,446,"Isn't that a bit cruel?"],[446,567,"I mean, she's just a child."],[567,675,"No one saw her do it."],[675,742,"We shouldn't be rushing"],[742,838,"to conclusions."],[838,963,"She's eight years old."],[963,1105,"She knows good from bad."],[1105,1242,"Kids gotta learn somehow."],[1242,1368,"Otherwise she'll never fit in."],[1401,1509,"If you don't catch them young,"],[1509,1622,"they'll only get worse."],[1622,1760,"The next time it'll be a snake."],[1797,1951,"Theft, arson,"],[2114,2189,"murder!"],[2189,2273,"Oh."],[2389,2598,"Brats like you need to be punished,"],[2648,2844,"so we can make sure that you learn"],[2844,2973,"a lesson."],[2973,3053,"No!"],[3094,3194,"Charlotte,"],[3194,3395,"I'm so disappointed in you."],[3399,3516,"I've never known"],[3516,3774,"an eight-year-old to be so evil,"],[3774,3983,"as to put a cockroach"],[3983,4133,"in someone's drink!"],[4154,4245,"If Raphael"],[4245,4396,"would've married my daughter,"],[4437,4583,"she would've been raised right."],[4592,4754,"None of this would have happened."],[4808,4892,"Hold her down."],[4921,4988,"Sorry, Miss-"],[4988,5217,"Hold her down or I will ruin you!"],[5701,5805,"Here comes"],[5805,6085,"the airplane! - No!"],[6097,6268,"Open your mouth!"]],"57":[[70,145,"Stop!"],[1430,1509,"Don't"],[1618,1755,"touch Charlotte."],[2043,2202,"So you're the stupid cripple that"],[2214,2352,"Raphael married."],[2352,2431,"Fess up."],[2431,2540,"You baby-trapped him."],[2552,2907,"And you stole my daughter's fiancé!"],[2944,3065,"What is she talking about?"],[3065,3269,"Isn't Lucy Raphael's wife?"],[3282,3549,"That's what she wants you to believe."],[3574,3666,"Because she doesn't want you"],[3666,3749,"to know the truth."]],"58":[[16,137,"The truth is that"],[187,408,"I knew the late Mrs. Stone"],[471,529,"very well."],[583,850,"And my biological daughter, Asteria,"],[880,967,"was promised"],[975,1130,"to be married to her son,"],[1176,1251,"Raphael."],[1280,1355,"But then..."],[1476,1609,"she went missing!"],[1651,1901,"Regina was then promised to Raphael."],[1935,2152,"Then along came Lucy."],[2173,2310,"She seduced Raphael,"],[2310,2435,"and then she had his baby."],[2469,2623,"And then she deliberately"],[2656,2831,"hid her child for years."],[2831,3019,"Just so she could bargain her way"],[3053,3199,"back into the Stone family,"],[3207,3474,"and I couldn't marry Raphael."],[3553,3603,"Is that"],[3603,3716,"what happened with Charlotte?"],[3716,3862,"No wonder it took so long"],[3862,3945,"to bring her back."],[3974,4062,"Shameless."],[4133,4266,"So Lucy's a home-wrecking"],[4266,4354,"gold-digger."],[4404,4512,"No, I..."],[4600,4671,"I'm..."],[4892,4996,"You're lying!"],[5013,5184,"Daddy said he was always gonna be"],[5184,5271,"with Mommy!"],[5288,5480,"You take that back!"],[5488,5547,"No!"],[5559,5755,"Mommy and Daddy love each other."],[5764,5910,"You're the home-wrecker!"],[5943,6093,"You little twerp!"]],"59":[[20,229,"You take that back."],[229,375,"You little twerp!"],[617,754,"Why do you have to be so mean?"],[754,892,"I'm gonna tell Daddy!"],[921,1113,"I'm gonna tell Daddy!"],[1113,1438,"News flash, Daddy doesn't care."],[1438,1555,"Your mom"],[1584,1847,"is just a silly social climber."],[1885,2010,"All she wants is money."],[2064,2314,"You two will never fit in."],[2373,2548,"You don't belong in high society."],[2602,2877,"Look here, little dumbo!"],[2936,3036,"You know what that is?"],[3240,3553,"It's a check for five million dollars."],[3603,3720,"And I know"],[3720,3837,"that you're in it for the money."],[3837,4083,"So just take it and scram."],[4204,4279,"Yeah,"],[4295,4416,"with that kind of money,"],[4416,4600,"you won't have to trick your way"],[4600,4750,"into people's homes anymore."],[4792,4900,"You're so stupid,"],[4900,5084,"you don't understand what it is?"],[5084,5309,"Or is it just too little?"],[5321,5534,"Daddy has more money than that!"],[5701,5776,"Fine."],[5847,6168,"There's a check for ten million more!"],[6656,6823,"So take your brat daughter,"],[6823,6965,"and get out of here."],[7044,7232,"I'm not gonna allow you to ruin"],[7278,7432,"my daughter's future."],[7465,7586,"Raphael's mother"],[7599,7895,"wanted my daughter to marry Raphael."],[7912,7982,"Yes."],[7999,8258,"This is your last chance, Lucy."],[8295,8429,"So you better take the money,"],[8458,8579,"or you'll be in big trouble."]],"60":[[0,171,"So you better take the money,"],[187,325,"or you'll be in big trouble."],[771,842,"No."],[867,946,"No money."],[1172,1334,"I will marry Raphael."],[1338,1397,"Oh."],[1547,1614,"Yeah!"],[1626,1730,"Mommy and Daddy"],[1730,1843,"are gonna get married!"],[1843,1981,"I don't want anything else!"],[1981,2252,"You think Raphael loves you?"],[2356,2531,"You just tried to poison me"],[2531,2652,"with cockroaches."],[2652,2802,"No, I didn't do that!"],[2831,2944,"Mommy and Daddy"],[2944,3103,"said they will love me, always."],[3103,3157,"Oh."],[3207,3561,"You are just a bastard child,"],[3607,3720,"born of an idiot mother."],[3770,3895,"What do you know about love?"],[3941,4179,"No, I know Mommy loves me."],[4220,4550,"Ugh, shut up, you twerp."],[5142,5413,"Don't touch my daugher..."],[5643,5718,"Bitch."],[6160,6331,"No, Mommy, wait!"],[6331,6414,"Stop!"]],"61":[[279,467,"You bitch, go away!"],[496,613,"Nobody likes you."],[646,880,"Raphael is only with you out of pity."],[934,1096,"One day he's going to kick you to the curb."],[1096,1276,"And I'll be his Mrs."],[1276,1405,"And I'm gonna beat your daughter"],[1405,1668,"black and blue every day."],[1926,2268,"Don't hurt Charlotte."],[2302,2431,"You bitch!"],[2469,2606,"I'm gonna fucking kill you!"],[2606,2711,"And make sure"],[2711,2915,"that you never get with Raphael!"],[2986,3144,"Don't touch my Mommy!"],[3962,4124,"Let go of her!"],[4300,4441,"No, Mommy!"],[4441,4558,"Don't hurt her!"]],"62":[[1751,1910,"Mommy, please don't die!"],[1910,1981,"Wake up."],[1981,2152,"Please don't die."],[2210,2410,"Mommy, I can't be alone."],[2473,2623,"Please wake up!"],[3983,4175,"Wait, am I cured?"]],"63":[[25,175,"Please wake up!"],[988,1184,"Wait, am I cured?"],[1897,1972,"Charlotte."],[2152,2235,"Mommy?"],[2344,2464,"I love you."],[3207,3307,"She thinks I'm dumb."],[3353,3490,"That I can't defend myself."],[3490,3603,"And in that case,"],[3624,3795,"I'll just go along with her plan."],[4045,4158,"Mommy, are you better?"],[5855,5976,"Hydrate"],[6056,6189,"or die-drate."],[6535,6669,"Ah!"],[6669,6744,"You lunatic!"]],"64":[[25,158,"Ah!"],[158,233,"You lunatic!"],[1230,1397,"Get that away from me!"],[1430,1518,"Pokey, pokey."],[1572,1730,"You want to play pokey, pokey?"],[1735,1976,"No, no pokey, pokey."],[1997,2122,"If I get hurt,"],[2147,2277,"Raphael is going to be"],[2277,2414,"super upset, okay?"],[2414,2719,"So just put down the knife."],[2786,2869,"Knife?"],[3048,3224,"Knife means cut!"],[3319,3407,"Oh, no!"],[3407,3495,"No, no, no, no, no."],[3703,3803,"No!"]],"65":[[296,371,"Lucy!"],[412,483,"No!"],[871,938,"It's okay."],[2281,2373,"It's okay."],[2823,2911,"It's okay."],[3023,3115,"Don't be scared."],[3236,3349,"Charlotte, what happened?"],[3374,3520,"It's the mean lady again."],[3520,3661,"She tried to kill Mommy."],[3661,3737,"No, no, that's-"],[3753,3945,"Raphael, that's not what happened."],[3945,4120,"I would never, ever-"],[4266,4496,"Raphael, what are you doing?"]],"66":[[254,458,"Mom, you tell him."],[513,679,"I accidentally shoved Lucy,"],[679,771,"and then she tried to"],[771,884,"kill me with a knife."],[905,988,"Raphael,"],[1026,1105,"how could you let"],[1105,1263,"this maniac run loose?"],[1305,1384,"You need to"],[1405,1555,"put her in a hospital or something"],[1555,1747,"until she knows how to behave herself."],[2097,2323,"Lucy, tell me the truth."],[2398,2502,"I'll believe you."],[2669,2911,"She tried to frame Charlotte"],[2911,3073,"for something that she didn't do."],[3090,3261,"And then she tried to replace me"],[3290,3374,"as your wife"],[3390,3611,"and abuse Charlotte after I'm gone."],[3691,3774,"Lucy."],[4104,4204,"You're back."],[4304,4371,"I am."],[5397,5459,"Stop!"],[5647,5818,"We have to talk."]],"67":[[717,996,"This is legit."],[1042,1305,"I never knew your mother signed this."],[1305,1438,"How do we know it's her signature?"],[1551,1697,"She put it in writing."],[1793,1897,"She promised"],[1943,2052,"Yvonne's daughter,"],[2110,2277,"that she would marry you"],[2331,2473,"if she wanted to."],[2540,2615,"And if not,"],[2648,2857,"we owe them twenty five billion"],[2857,3048,"dollars in assets."],[3507,3666,"I'm so sorry, Charlotte."],[3753,3899,"But if we could just spend another day"],[3899,4120,"with your dad, as a happy family,"],[4200,4291,"it would be enough."],[4391,4625,"Here Mommy, here's a beautiful flower"],[4625,4763,"for a beautiful person."],[5555,5772,"Asteria, if you're still alive,"],[5968,6143,"just please know that mommy will"],[6156,6306,"always love you."]],"68":[[563,621,"Asteria?"],[621,779,"You're my Asteria?"],[921,1080,"I, uh..."],[1088,1255,"I don't know what you're talking about."],[1714,1814,"You're my daughter."],[2189,2252,"Lucy,"],[2356,2456,"are you adopted?"],[2619,2986,"Um, my parents adopted me"],[2986,3165,"from an orphanage when I was six."],[3165,3428,"But I don't know my biological parents."],[3457,3616,"Well, we'll have to make sure."],[3695,3933,"But, if you're Asteria,"],[3933,4066,"then there's no problem"],[4095,4279,"with you marrying Raphael."],[4346,4491,"You're, you're really mine."],[4587,4850,"I know you probably don't trust me."],[4913,5071,"But I will give you"],[5071,5255,"as much time as you need."],[5380,5551,"Your inheritance, all of it,"],[5613,5755,"I've saved it for you."],[5809,5989,"Lucy, you don't have to worry."],[6197,6252,"Well, okay."],[6289,6377,"You stay here."],[6652,6911,"I've always wanted a little granddaughter."]],"69":[[191,333,"Well, Lucy."],[375,500,"You must be mighty"],[500,663,"satisfied with yourself."],[709,963,"First, you steal my fiancé."],[1026,1172,"Now you're gonna take my mother"],[1172,1301,"and everything"],[1301,1443,"that's supposed to be mine?"],[1488,1705,"Is money really all you care about?"],[1789,1956,"Yvonne spent her whole life"],[1956,2097,"treating you as her own,"],[2143,2264,"giving you everything"],[2264,2373,"that money could buy."],[2435,2598,"While I was out on the street,"],[2648,2806,"digging through garbage,"],[2806,2952,"just to have my next meal."],[2952,3073,"Just to survive."],[3082,3253,"Is that really not enough for you?"],[3294,3436,"I won't be satisfied"],[3436,3591,"until I have everything."],[3636,3737,"Sorry, sister."],[3807,3987,"But I guess you'll have to settle for half"],[3987,4041,"Shut up!"],[4099,4270,"Why did you have to come back?"],[4312,4462,"Why did it have to be you?"],[4554,4679,"Why did you ruin my life?"],[4679,4854,"You ruined everything!"]],"70":[[20,191,"Why did you have to come back?"],[225,375,"Why did it have to be you?"],[471,600,"Why did you ruin my life?"],[600,775,"You ruined everything!"],[821,892,"Go to hell!"],[1443,1568,"Ah!"],[1647,1730,"Lucy?"]],"71":[[729,817,"She gonna be okay?"],[1906,2006,"I remember."],[2039,2198,"Raphael, I, I remember."],[2431,2498,"The accident."],[2498,2556,"It..."],[2773,2861,"It was Regina."],[3324,3495,"From seven years ago?"],[3574,3812,"I saw Regina behind the wheel of the car."],[3849,3928,"It was her."],[4049,4262,"Regina, how could you?"],[4346,4471,"I mean, playing a"],[4500,4713,"game in a social way is one thing but"],[4767,4950,"trying to murder someone?"],[4988,5150,"Please tell me it isn't true."]],"72":[[4,162,"Please tell me it isn't true!"],[658,784,"So what if I did?"],[975,1130,"Would you even try to defend me?"],[1205,1455,"I loved you like my own daughter."],[1559,1668,"I didn't know that I was"],[1672,1814,"raising a murderer!"],[1814,1906,"Shut up!"],[2022,2139,"You never loved me."],[2231,2360,"I was just there"],[2381,2527,"to make you feel better"],[2527,2640,"after your bio daughter"],[2640,2715,"went missing."],[2773,2965,"As soon as Asteria showed up,"],[3015,3090,"you were gonna give her"],[3090,3199,"all of your assets."],[3240,3349,"I heard everything."],[3445,3524,"And you."],[3645,3824,"You're pathetic!"],[3895,4145,"Do you know how much money"],[4145,4312,"I spent on that"],[4333,4604,"post-grad fake Harvard degree?"],[4688,4829,"And how hard it was"],[4829,4992,"to pretend to like you?"],[5030,5209,"Oh, and those cockroaches"],[5209,5363,"were disgusting."],[5413,5563,"You didn't appreciate it."],[5563,5663,"Take her away."],[5726,5772,"No."],[5772,5889,"I hate you!"],[5889,6022,"You're gonna spend the rest of your life"],[6022,6143,"in prison where you belong!"],[6151,6218,"I hate you!"],[6218,6314,"Take her now!"],[6314,6398,"I hate you!"],[6485,6602,"Now who's useless?"],[6602,6673,"Shut up!"],[7186,7278,"She okay?"],[7353,7482,"She's a strong woman."],[7482,7582,"She'll be fine."]],"73":[[154,275,"I need you to breathe, alright?"],[287,408,"Breathe, breathe."],[446,588,"Okay, I see a head."],[588,729,"I need a good push, alright?"],[771,825,"Push!"],[846,1046,"Ah!"],[1046,1317,"Oh, it's a boy!"],[3249,3370,"Regina Lawrence."],[3440,3516,"You're under arrest."],[3516,3582,"No!"],[3582,3678,"I, I, I'm innocent! - Yeah."],[3732,3828,"I'm an heiress!"],[3832,3916,"I'm innocent!"],[3916,3991,"Yeah,"],[3991,4116,"and I'm Superman, come on."],[5096,5242,"And by the power vested in me,"],[5242,5409,"I now pronounce you man"],[5438,5526,"and wife."],[5588,5676,"Raphael,"],[5697,5834,"you may kiss the bride."]]}